{"data":[{"date":"15:27 21/07","title":"HLV Emery si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, Ozil h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/29/hlv-emery-thiet-chat-ky-luat-ozil-hoi-quan-som-cung-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng Arsenal.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf HLV Wenger d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal, HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/HLV-Unai-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-Mesut-Ozil-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt \u1edf Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd tr\u00ean TTCN, t\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra g\u1ea7n 80 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 5 t\u00e2n binh. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1t s\u1edbm k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm gi\u00fap HLV Emery c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd mang theo nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t cho Arsenal, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEmry \u0111ang si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Arsenal \u0111ang t\u1eadp r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1edbi 8h t\u1ed1i. C\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ef1u HLV PSG \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mesut Ozil h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ozil\" title=\"Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/29/hlv-emery-thiet-chat-ky-luat-ozil-hoi-quan-som-cung-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ozil tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p Mesut Ozil, b\u1edfi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i bay t\u1edbi Singapore v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 22/07\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNgo\u00e0i Ozil th\u00ec Mohamed Elneny v\u00e0 Alex Iwobi c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Ozil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Arsenal, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1485","checkdouble":"191732"},{"date":"15:23 21/07","title":"Man City th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, Guardiola v\u1eabn h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/HLV-Guardiola.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City m\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Borussia Dortmund trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Pep Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19. H\u1ecd so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Borussia Dortmund t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Soldier Field (Chicago, M\u1ef9) trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Cup Champions.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Kevin De Bruyne, Raheem Sterling, David Silva, Vincent Kompany, Bernardo Silva, Sergio Aguero hay Gabriel Jesus. V\u00ec th\u1ebf t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ed3n v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a The Citizens.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pep Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pep Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/HLV-Pep-Guardiola-hai-long-voi-cau-thu-Man-City-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mahrez ra m\u1eaft Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i v\u00e0 uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh Dortmund \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ec9 m\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Algeria kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e1nh n\u1ed5i Man City g\u1ed3m \u0111a ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. H\u1ecd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund b\u1edfi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Mario Gotze.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund, HLV Pep Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City. \u201cT\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y song hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i\u201d, Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng nhau v\u00e0 h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nhau.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Guardiola\" title=\"HLV Guardiola\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/HLV-Guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Guardiola h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 can \u0111\u1ea3m, s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao \u0111\u1ed9. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ee7a Dortmund. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-tu-tin-soan-ngoi-man-city-172-191690.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool t\u1ef1 tin so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-chia-tay-sterling-172-191666.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rooney-phat-bieu-ve-mu-va-cuoc-dua-vo-dich-172-191513.html\">Rooney tin M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 Man City m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/joe-hart-sang-my-du-dau-cung-man-city-172-191439.html\">Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea9u, Hart \u201cmu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t\u201d sang M\u1ef9 du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-bo-cuoc-vu-mateo-kovacic-172-191406.html\">\u0110\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c v\u1ee5 Mateo Kovacic</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1484","checkdouble":"191733"},{"date":"15:59 21/07","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Liverpool s\u1eafp chia tay Danny Ings","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/21/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-liverpool-sap-chia-tay-danny-ings.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng The Kop tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 di chuy\u1ec3n sang M\u1ef9 tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018, The Kop s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Klopp th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng tham gia du \u0111\u1ea5u, Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng tham gia du \u0111\u1ea5u, Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/21/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-liverpool-sap-chia-tay-danny-ings.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Ings kh\u00f4ng tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Dortmund v\u00e0o 3h05 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam).</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch 29 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba Mohamed Salah, Sadio Mane v\u00e0 Marko Grujic \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. 4 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng b\u1ed9 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi ng\u1edd r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Ings. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Danny Ings s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng tham gia du \u0111\u1ea5u, Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng tham gia du \u0111\u1ea5u, Danny Ings r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/20/danny-ings-thua-nhan-hoc-theo-firmino-de-lay-lai-phong-do-tot-nhat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Ings s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDanny Ings chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool t\u1eeb Burnley c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 3 n\u0103m, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Brendan Rodgers \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao, song ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u cho Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Klopp, Ings c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i r\u1ea5t ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 25 l\u1ea7n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Burnley t\u1edbi Liverpool, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c The Kop \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ings \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Anfield. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Crystal Palace, Celtic, Southampton v\u00e0 Bournemouth.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/southampton-chi-20-trieu-bang-mua-tien-dao-cua-liverpool-172-191262.html\" target=\"_blank\">Southampton mua Danny Ings</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 cao nh\u1ea5t, Daily Echo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary chi 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1483","checkdouble":"191735"},{"date":"16:48 21/07","title":"T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/jeremie-boga-roi-chelsea-toi-sassuolo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jeremie Boga r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Sassuolo. Sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho 3 CLB kh\u00e1c nhau m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong th\u1eddi gian qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB Serie A mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Boga li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJeremie Boga sinh ng\u00e0y 3 th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 1997 t\u1ea1i Marseille trong m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh g\u1ed1c B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0. Anh gia nh\u1eadp l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t CLB nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c trinh s\u00e1t vi\u00ean Chelsea ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 n\u0103m 2009. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay, Boga ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Chelsea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a The Blues t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, song c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 18 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Christensen v\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 Gary Cahill nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jeremie Boga r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Sassuolo gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jeremie Boga r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Sassuolo gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/jeremie-boga-roi-chelsea-toi-sassuolo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jeremie Boga r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Sassuolo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3, Boga li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh n\u00e0y l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t t\u1edbi Rennes (Ph\u00e1p), Granada (T\u00e2y Ban Nha) r\u1ed3i Birmingham (Anh).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Sassuolo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u00f9a 2017/18, Boga nh\u1eafn l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecb cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 21, anh tin m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 Boga r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Sassuolo. Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp CLB c\u1ee7a Serie A theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Theo gi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin, m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed Sassuolo b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Boga r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 3.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18, Sassuolo x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 11 tr\u00ean BXH Serie A. Boga l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 8 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd sau nh\u1eefng Federico Di Francesco, Khouma Babacar, Jens Odgaard, Mehdi Bourabia, Leonardo Sernicola, Filip Djuricic v\u00e0 Kevin-Prince Boateng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-se-ban-kante-cho-psg-neu-172-191721.html\">Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u00e1n Kante cho PSG n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\">G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n 3, Barca quy\u1ebft mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-tu-choi-phu-phang-de-nghi-chuyen-nhuong-cua-chelsea-172-191702.html\">Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-quan-tam-toi-jasper-cillessen-172-191681.html\">S\u1ee3 Real 'c\u01b0\u1edbp' ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Chelsea v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua sao Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1482","checkdouble":"191736"},{"date":"16:22 21/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 21/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/chuyen-nhuong-mu-hot-nhat-ngay-2107.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 21/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2107 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2107 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U kh\u00f4ng mua Alderweireld \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham. V\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Alderweireld v\u1edbi Spurs ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, khi \u0111\u00f3 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld-172-191725.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld-172-191725.html\">Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alderweireld?</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Toby Alderweireld, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua ng\u00f4i sao...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Matteo Darmian c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi M.U v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Metteo Darmian \u0111ang c\u00f9ng M.U tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e8 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, song ESPN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Old Trafford. Hi\u1ec7n Roma, Inter Milan v\u00e0 Juventus l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ef1u sao Torino.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng cho Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale se quyet tam chung to minh khi Ronaldo ra di\" title=\"Bale s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/HLV-Lopetegui-quyet-khong-de-Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-Madrid--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Bale h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Gareth Bale. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Bill Rice c\u1ee7a BBC HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb BL\u0110 M.U mua th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eefa trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Eric Bailly</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Express kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Eric Bailly, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Old&nbsp;Trafford v\u00ec m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng hot World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hirving Lozano gieo rac con ac mong cho DT Duc.\" title=\"Hirving Lozano gieo r\u1eafc c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/DT-Duc-thua-soc-truoc-Mexico-Low-da-thuc-su-het-bai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hirving Lozano s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o H\u00e0 Lan Eindhovens Dagblad, ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Hirving Lozano ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Old Trafford \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3 PSV Eindhoven \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU kh\u00f4ng mua Robert Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mua Robert Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alex Sandro&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alex Sandro c\u1ee7a Juventus l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a PSG, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U v\u1ee5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1481","checkdouble":"191737"},{"date":"17:13 21/07","title":"Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 danh t\u00ednh h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 MU ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/video-tong-hop-mu-11-club-america-giao-huu-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn Man Utd vs Leicester t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u ng\u00e0y 10/8, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Premier League 2018/19.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u0103m nay, Man Utd v\u00e0 Leicester s\u1ebd l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf Premier League 2018/19 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u ng\u00e0y 10/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Old Trafford. V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c, Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u00f4i \u0111u\u00f4i l\u1ecdt cho h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester khai m\u1ea1c Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester khai m\u1ea1c Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/video-tong-hop-mu-11-club-america-giao-huu-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 danh t\u00ednh h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 trong tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester khai m\u1ea1c Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edf m\u00e0n s\u1edbm h\u01a1n th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 c\u1eadp r\u1eadp ch\u1ec9 sau ch\u01b0a tr\u00f2n m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac World Cup 2018, s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn HLV Jose Mourinho t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u trong v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh, B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p (Pogba, Lukaku, Fellaini, Lingard, Rashford, Young, Jones).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 danh t\u00ednh b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c: \u201cAntonio Valencia, Chris Smalling, Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Luke Shaw \u2013 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester.\u201d \u2013 Ecuador c\u1ee7a Valencia v\u00e0 B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Bailly kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, trong khi Smalling v\u00e0 Shaw kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean Tam S\u01b0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1edbm h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y Mourinho kh\u00f3 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh gia c\u1ed1 khu v\u1ef1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-utd-chua-gi-da-mat-tan-binh-vi-chan-thuong-172-191570.html\" target=\"_blank\">h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i 19 tu\u1ed5i Diogo Dalot d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai th\u00e1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean IC Cup tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Club America. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e2m n\u00f3ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 San Jose Earthquakes, AC Milan, Liverpool, Real Madrid v\u00e0 Bayern Munich.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-club-america-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191627.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/mu-vs-club-america-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-club-america-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191627.html\">MU 1-1 Club America (KT): Juan Mata c\u1ee9u Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf h\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Mexico. Juan Mata l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1480","checkdouble":"191738"},{"date":"17:55 21/07","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 SLNA vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/ket-qua-slna-vs-hagl-tran-dau-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 SLNA vs HAGL tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, video b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, clip highlights tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u SLNA S\u00f4ng Lam Ngh\u1ec7 An vs HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/7.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10.5pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 hi\u1ec7p 1: SLNA 2-0 HAGL<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Olaha (13'), Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh (45'+2).</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, c\u1ea3 SLNA vs HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 hai, Olaha x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u00e1 hay b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i r\u1ed3i t\u1ea1t v\u00e0o trong cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i h\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"SLNA vs HAGL\" title=\"SLNA vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/6_Zing_3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>SLNA thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n HAGL trong hi\u1ec7p 1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 SLNA ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i \u0111i thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, HAGL v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Olaha \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 13 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olaha v\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm gi\u00fap tr\u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi d\u00f9 Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc hay C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nguy hi\u1ec3m. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7p 1 s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a SLNA th\u00ec \u0111\u00fang \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 2, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap SLNA v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau 45 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;color:#222222;mso-fareast-language:KO\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1479","checkdouble":"191739"},{"date":"17:41 21/07","title":"Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i thay Iniesta cho Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/xavi-tien-cu-rabiot-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Rabiot cho Barca. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia m\u1edbi chia tay b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paulinho, Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Xavi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Barca mua Rabiot</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho hay Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1ebd chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kho\u1ea3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho ra \u0111i l\u1ea1i c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1eefng Andre Gomes hay Denis Suarez g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1. Xavi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Blaugrana tin r\u1eb1ng Rabiot s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Rabiot cho Barca trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Iniesta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Rabiot cho Barca trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Iniesta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/xavi-tien-cu-rabiot-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt\u201d, Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Rabiot cho Barca tr\u00ean t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o t\u1ea1i Barca. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u1ebfu gia nh\u1eadp.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Griezmann r\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico. N\u1ebfu h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Rabiot ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho Barca.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i Arthur</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 Arthur Melo t\u1eeb Gremio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 39 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Xavi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 DNA c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia song tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho anh n\u1ebfu b\u1ecb so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh hay Iniesta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xavi cua Barca\" title=\"Xavi cua Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Xavi-cua-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed Rabiot cho Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i video v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Arthur. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil t\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Aspire (Qatar) \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Al Sadd n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho Barca. Arthur c\u00f3 c\u00e1i m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 DNA Barca.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f9ng xem Arthur c\u00f3 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn hay ch\u01b0a. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Barca l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\">\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\">G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n 3, Barca quy\u1ebft mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-digne-chuan-bi-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-172-191654.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-bao-tin-cuc-vui-cho-mu-va-barca-172-191646.html\">Sao kh\u1ee7ng Chelsea b\u00e1o tin c\u1ef1c vui cho MU v\u00e0 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ajax-gui-canh-bao-danh-thep-toi-barca-180-191626.html\">Nh\u0103m nhe sao tr\u1ebb, Barca nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u1eaft t\u1eeb Ajax</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1478","checkdouble":"191740"},{"date":"17:01 21/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Bayern Munich vs PSG 21h05 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/21/bayern-munich-vs-psg-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Bayern Munich vs PSG: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Bayern vs PSG gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018 l\u00fac 21h05 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPH\u00c1T BI\u1ec2U<br>\r\nHLV Niko Kovac (Bayern): \u201cPSG l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Bayern\u201d.<br>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel (PSG): \u201cTh\u1eadt vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p Bayern trong t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a PSG. T\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c, Bayern l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1. Nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, PSG c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1 1 t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00fa v\u1ecb\u201d.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Bayern Munich vs PSG t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 217 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Bayern Munich vs PSG t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 217 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/nhan-dinh-bayern-munich-vs-psg-21h05-ngay-217-icc-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bayern Munich vs PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN<br>\r\n- Bayern to\u00e0n thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb 2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n- 9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Bayern, c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 7 tr\u1eadn c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong 2 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Champions League 2017/18.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1eb5n: 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Bayern, c\u00f3 3 tr\u1eadn k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ch\u1eb5n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, 11 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a PSG c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 9 tr\u1eadn k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung l\u00e0 ch\u1eb5n. K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n tr\u00ean s\u1ebd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1477","checkdouble":"191741"},{"date":"09:52 21/07","title":"Keita: \"T\u00f4i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Bayern v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/keita-toi-tu-choi-bayern-va-barca-de-den-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Naby Keita kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Barcelona hay Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool.</h2><h2>Keita gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-dat-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-naby-keita-172-167150.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Guinea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Leipzig t\u1edbi Liverpool</span> t\u1eeb n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 48 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ba ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Jordan Henderson v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Fabinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Naby Keita \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barcelona v\u00e0 Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho The Kop.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Keita gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool sau khi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Bayern v\u00e0 Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Keita gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool sau khi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Bayern v\u00e0 Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/keita-toi-tu-choi-bayern-va-barca-de-den-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Keita gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool sau khi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Bayern v\u00e0 Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi t\u00f4i nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp\u201d, Keita tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi sau khi t\u1edd Guardian h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Barcelona v\u00e0 Bayern Munich. \u201cNh\u01b0ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o HLV Klopp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t. Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1ecb thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nhanh t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u v\u1edbi Mane v\u1ec1 Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMane c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh trai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 9 th\u00e1ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau t\u1ea1i Salzburg v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a nhau k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3. Anh \u1ea5y k\u1ec3 cho t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng Liverpool \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Keita t\u1ef1 tin khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Keita th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Bundesliga. \u1ede Premier League, va ch\u1ea1m m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng Keita kh\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Premier League s\u1ebd ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n anh t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u1edf Premier League c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c t\u1edbi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSuy ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n l\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ea1n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNgo\u00e0i ra, n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n th\u00ec t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi vinh quang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-tu-tin-soan-ngoi-man-city-172-191690.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool t\u1ef1 tin so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-alisson-toi-liverpool-172-191677.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1476","checkdouble":"191715"},{"date":"10:33 21/07","title":"Totti: \"Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u1edf v\u1ee5 Alisson\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/totti-liverpool-da-dua-ra-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-o-vu-alisson.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Totti th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Roma bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Alisson khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1eeb l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</h2><h2>Alisson \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool v\u1edbi ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool</span> theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mang v\u1ec1 cho Roma 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Alisson l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Roma c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 chung cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i Serie A c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u1edf v\u1ee5 Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u1edf v\u1ee5 Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/totti-liverpool-da-dua-ra-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-o-vu-alisson.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Totti cho r\u1eb1ng Roma kh\u00f3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Liverpool cho Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Totti cho r\u1eb1ng Roma kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho d\u00f9 Alisson th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang ta \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1ed5 sung s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Roma c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAlisson \u01b0? Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. 75 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u1edbi x\u1ea3y ra l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc khi Roma m\u1ea5t \u0111i m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Alisson tri \u00e2n Roma</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c g\u1eedi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi tri \u00e2n t\u1edbi Roma, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i anh t\u1edbi to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi Roma. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7y th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ebd v\u1ec1 hai h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00e1c nhau. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi: CLB, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Roma \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean t\u00f4i trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn, m\u1ecdi n\u1ed1t th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m v\u00e0 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef CLB Roma c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 trong tr\u00e1i tim m\u00ecnh\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Alisson:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-xay-ra-sau-khi-liverpool-chieu-mo-alisson-becker-172-191685.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau khi Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson Becker</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-alisson-toi-liverpool-172-191677.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson t\u1edbi Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1475","checkdouble":"191716"},{"date":"10:51 21/07","title":"Herrera ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do De Gea \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/21/herrera-tiet-lo-ly-do-de-gea-o-lai-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ander Herrera cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n De Gea \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</h2><h2>De Gea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real, \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh De Gea v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Real Madrid k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 sau khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2015. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Real m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay. Thibaut Courtois c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Herrera ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do De Gea \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Herrera ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do De Gea \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/herrera-tiet-lo-ly-do-de-gea-o-lai-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Herrera kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh De Gea \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU v\u00ec t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ander Herrera cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u gi\u1eef <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/de-gea-phu-voi-real-quyet-o-lai-mu-172-187702.html\" target=\"_blank\">De Gea \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1edb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi De Gea khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e1t vang t\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Sau \u0111\u00f3, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cDe Gea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u0103m n\u00e0y qua n\u0103m kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0o gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n De Gea. Th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 nh\u1edd v\u1eady m\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Herrera b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 De Gea sau World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau khi ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua \u1edf World Cup 2018. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, De Gea c\u00f2n m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 3-3 v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Herrera tin r\u1eb1ng De Gea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m c\u00e2m l\u1eb7ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Man United \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. T\u00f4i nh\u1edb khi t\u00f4i c\u00f2n \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn Man United. Nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 sau 4 n\u0103m, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i may m\u1eafn khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c De Gea v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m nh\u1eefng chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec. Khi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng De Gea th\u00ec kh\u00e1c, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-217-dai-dien-sao-psg-lien-he-voi-mu-184-191700.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 21/7: \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n sao PSG li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-cau-thu-mu-nen-thanh-ly-ngay-he-nay-172-191686.html\">4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU n\u00ean thanh l\u00fd ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1474","checkdouble":"191718"},{"date":"07:03 21/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 18h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (V-League 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/nhan-dinh-nam-dinh-vs-quang-nam-18h00-ngay-217-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam l\u00fac 18h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7 (V\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam V-League 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 18h00 ng\u00e0y 217 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam 18h00 ng\u00e0y 217 V-League 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/quangnam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: 4-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>T\u1eeb ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u00f3ng \u0111inh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i BXH\u00a0V-League 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u201cng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 khi m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng b\u01b0\u1edbc sang giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1. 7 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9 ch\u1ec9 thua 2, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 2, thu v\u1ec1 11/21 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a. Trong khi c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb 2 v\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam ch\u1ec9 ki\u1ebfm v\u1ebbn v\u1eb9n 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1edbi 3-0 song r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, s\u1ef1 non k\u00e9m kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn (b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 3-3).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi khu v\u1ef1c nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1edd h\u01a1n ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. Chi\u1ec1u nay, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea3nh th\u01a1i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i h\u01a1n 1 th\u00e1ng (tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Asiad 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi). Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m tay th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u0103ng hoa \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2017, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u nay, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 6 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac m\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n ca kh\u00fac kh\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 2, thua 5. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 3 tr\u1eadn, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 0, thua 2.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 0, thua 0. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nNam \u0110\u1ecbnh: Qu\u1ed1c Thi\u1ec7n Esele; V\u0103n Qu\u00fd, Vi\u1ebft T\u00fa, H\u1eefu Qu\u00fd, M\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Kortzorg, H\u1eefu \u0110\u1ecbnh, S\u1ef9 Minh, Diogo, Minh Tu\u1ea5n.<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3ng Nam: V\u0103n C\u01b0\u1eddng; V\u0103n Phong, Ng\u1ecdc Nguy\u00ean, V\u0103n H\u00e0, T\u1ea5n Sinh, Thanh Trung, \u0110\u00ecnh Th\u1eafng, Huy H\u00f9ng, Quang Huy, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, Oliveira.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1473","checkdouble":"191707"},{"date":"07:11 21/07","title":"M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ch\u01b0a b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 tranh th\u1ee7 \u201cn\u1ecbnh\u201d t\u00e2n HLV Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/5/9/mua-giai-chua-bat-dau-fabregas-da-tranh-thu-ninh-tan-hlv-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Cesc Fabregas m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea, \u00f4ng Maurizio Sarri.</h2><h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2>Cesc Fabregas khen&nbsp;ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<p>Maurizio Sarri&nbsp;l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t ng\u1ed3i l\u00ean chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng HLV CLB Chelsea, sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd, Antonio Conte v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 5 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, HLV Sarri t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng t\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Napoli v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m l\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n theo \u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga Roman Abramovich.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"sarri\" title=\"sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/hlv-sarri-chi-ra-vi-tri-yeu-nhat-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Cesc Fabregas khen ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho t\u00e0i ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m n\u00e0y, Fabregas cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi! \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00edch n\u00f3.&nbsp;T\u00f4i l\u1edbn l\u00ean trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, trong ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u00f3 d\u00e0nh cho m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n trong m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00ec v\u1eady \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e8 n\u1eb7ng l\u00ean HLV Sarri ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Napoli. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Chelsea c\u1ee7a Sarri l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi Chelsea s\u1ebd d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi Man City. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm nh\u01b0ng d\u0129 nhi\u00ean HLV Sarri c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1472","checkdouble":"191709"},{"date":"08:00 21/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7): Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/nhan-dinh-slna-vs-hagl-17h00-ngay-217-ghi-diem-truoc-khi-len-tuyen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a NHM b\u1edfi d\u00e0n sao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u b\u00ean n\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp trung trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa?</h2><h2>Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">SLNA vs HAGL l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 hai b\u00ean kh\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c &ndash; Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u00f2n b\u00ean ph\u00eda HAGL c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Vinh trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng SLNA lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e1u l\u1eeda v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, c\u1ea3 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eabn Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft th\u1ea7y Park, b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 217) Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 217) Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/Nhan-dinh-SLNA-vs-HAGL-(17h00-ngay-217)-Ghi-diem-truoc-khi-len--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u00eat Nam \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn&nbsp;SLNA vs HAGL s\u1eafp t\u1edbi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean BXH, m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft th\u1ea7y Park tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">8 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp cho ASIAD 2018 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i CLB HAGL. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n c\u0169ng \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Vinh s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111ang chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB SLNA l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c. Ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu hai l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ed7i 7 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong th\u1eddi gian qua. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7y m\u00ea ho\u1eb7c, l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. C\u00f4ng c\u01b0\u1eddng, th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u01b0 H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 tr\u00ean BXH. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi HAGL s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd n\u00e2ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 8. SLNA \u0111ang &lsquo;bay cao&rsquo; nh\u1edd v\u00e0o c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 1 n\u1ed9i 1 ngo\u1ea1i: Michael Olaha v\u00e0 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong chu\u1ed7i 7 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a CLB.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, SLNA c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung V\u0103n B\u00ecnh t\u1eeb FLC Thanh H\u00f3a khi\u1ebfn cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 217) Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh SLNA vs HAGL (17h00 ng\u00e0y 217) Ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/truc-tiep-hagl-vs-slna-17h00-ngay-265-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB HAGL th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL gi\u00fap h\u1ecd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean HAGL v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Trong nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Vinh \u1edf 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 tay tr\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015 v\u00e0 2017, Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai &ldquo;\u00f4m h\u1eadn&rdquo; v\u1edbi c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. Trong khi m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2016 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-0 c\u0169ng nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. Do v\u1eady n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, HAGL ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh \u0111\u00e3 khi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u0103n nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a HAGL. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA trong c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 21/7. Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd theo d\u00f5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 20 V-League 2018\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Vong-20-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>SLNA: </strong>V\u0169 H\u1ea3i; Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u00ecnh Ho\u00e0ng, V\u0103n Kh\u00e1nh, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, Xu\u00e2n Th\u1eafng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Lynch, Olaha.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>HAGL: </strong>V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n S\u01a1n, A S\u00e2n, A Ho\u00e0ng, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, V\u0103n Thanh, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Osmar, Zeba Josip</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: SLNA 2-1 HAGL<br>\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl-168-191655.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/14/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-vong-20-vleague-dai-chien-slna-hagl-168-191655.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 20 V-League: \u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn SLNA &ndash; HAGL</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 20 V-League 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ed3n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa SLNA vs HAGL, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1471","checkdouble":"191711"}]}